data.description: Price Improvement!  Don't miss out!  Welcome home to this gorgeous 3/2  block and stucco Maple designer home with a golf cart garage.  It  looks a little like a Amarillo floorplan, has a double vaulted ceiling and has been extended in the back.. This home is located in the Village of Piedmont on a cul-de-sac street.  You will notice the nice painted driveway and walkway and lush landscape. Once you enter the leaded blue front door  ( with screen), you will be amazed at all of the wonderful upgrades.  Did I say TURNKEY?  Everything in this home stays except personal items and computers and printers.  There may be a few items which have dots on them that will not stay.  The Bond is Paid. the entire home is tiled except the two guest bedrooms which are luxury vinyl planking, and there is crown molding in the living area.  The ceilings are vaulted,  The living room has a sleeper sofa and  love seat and a chair.  In the dining room you will find a nice glass table with 4 chairs.  The kitchen has been redone and has a tiered high definition counter with loads of extra storage.  This home has stainless steel appliances and a gas range.  Notice the nice back splash and the updated sink and faucet.  The. Florida room is where you will enjoy most of your time on the huge power sectional.  Cooleroo shades in this room and the fireplace and fancy ceiling fan complete a beautiful look for this room.  To the right of this room is a small acrylic enclosed room for the person who wants to read or enjoy a peaceful time.  It has its own portable a/c unit. To the left of the Florida Room is the office area with plenty of storage and a desk.  Off this room is the screened lanai with a table and chairs and looks out onto the fun back yard with its own 5 hole putting green and viewing area from the two chairs under the umbrella.  On the side of the house is the grill and the pavered patio.  Come back inside and enjoy the nice Master bedroom with lots of furniture and a king size bed.  The Master bath has been redone with two beautiful vessel sinks and a tiled shower higher toilet, and two closets.  This split floor plan has two guest bedrooms each with  a closet .  Disney lovers will certianly enjoy the Mickey room complete a King Mickey bed and a Mickey rug.  The other guest bedroom has a pretty queen bed and also has a closet.  The Guest bath has been redone and has a fabulous shower, corian countertop, higher toilet, and new faucet.  The laundry room is so unique with its paneled wall, pull down screen to hide the a/c and many storage areas.  This home is perfect for a rental or a snow bird . 3 Solar tube.   New roof and gutters 2023, Stucco painted 2023, HVAC 2022.  Includes refrigerator in garage.  Taxes, $1883.44, Assmt includes fire $1259.13, NO BOND  4 seater Gas Yamaha Golf cart is included in turn key.  Personal items in garage may not be included. Other golf cart is not included.
